// App Gateway - Instance Count Over Time
// Counts the number of distinct App Gateway instances active in each 5-minute
// window and renders a timechart. Use this to visually identify scale-out and
// scale-in events during a load or performance test.
// Tip: Zoom into the test window in the timechart to see exactly when scaling
// occurred relative to the load profile.
AGWAccessLogs
| summarize InstanceCount = dcount(InstanceId) by bin(TimeGenerated, 5m)
| render timechart